      "id": "diverging-bounds-check",
      "durationMs": 18000,
      "narration": {
        "text": "Array bounds checks were not expensive by themselves. The failure helper returned into the loop, leaving a reachable call on every cycle. Making the throw path leave the method let clang hoist array metadata. Quicksort fell below HotSpot while keeping every check."
